items.description: This Python project analyzes the 2024 Indian Lok Sabha election data. It includes data cleaning, preprocessing, and exploratory data analysis (EDA) using visualizations like bar charts, pie charts, and heatmaps. The project also generates synthetic demographic data to gain deeper insights into voter behavior and trends.
